    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7629429/" class="title-link">贪嗔痴慢皆是毒，爱恨情仇必有欠</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7629429"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/34650878/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u34650878-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/34650878/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">蓝莓兔子</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-10-17"
      class="main-meta">2015-10-17 15:37:38</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7629429_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  文／蓝莓兔子  这几年的本土悬疑推理小说中，《清明上河图密码1》算得上是一部重磅诚意之作。作者冶文彪自成一派，以千年古画为基础，以史料为素材的表现形式颇为新颖，而环环相扣的布局，引人入胜的故事更是令这本书在年初大放异彩，令一众读者心甘情愿地纷纷跳坑。  据作者介...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7629429/#comments">(7回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">12有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
