  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7604792/" class="title-link">《清明上河图密码Ⅱ》3点小看法</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7604792"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/51297351/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u51297351-9.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/51297351/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">同学，西瓜掉了</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-09-21"
      class="main-meta">2015-09-21 21:01:07</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7604792_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                    这几天晚上和午休期间，把冶文彪的这本《清明上河图密码Ⅱ》看完了，因为对Ⅰ的认可，所以对于Ⅱ我确实报了些许的期待。看完第一遍后，除了结尾处稍显仓促外，感觉依旧不错。只是第一部作案动机的家国情仇到了第二部似乎主要成了私人恩怨，前面的勾心斗角水准出色，虽然手法...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7604792/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">7有用 / 1没用</span>
